07:19:50.099 --> 07:19:56.700
Hi, this is Tooey Sutherland.

07:19:56.759 --> 07:19:59.759
A Nightwing Guide to the Dragons of

07:19:59.759 --> 07:20:00.419
Pyrhea.

07:20:00.479 --> 07:20:02.459
Sandwings.

07:20:02.520 --> 07:20:06.180
Description, pale gold or white scales

07:20:06.180 --> 07:20:07.680
the color of desert sand.

07:20:07.740 --> 07:20:10.979
Poisonous barbed tail, forked black

07:20:10.979 --> 07:20:11.639
tongues.

07:20:11.759 --> 07:20:15.419
Abilities, can survive a long time

07:20:15.419 --> 07:20:15.900
without water.

07:20:15.959 --> 07:20:18.299
Poison enemies with the tips of their

07:20:18.299 --> 07:20:21.000
tails like scorpions, bury themselves for

07:20:21.000 --> 07:20:22.380
camouflage in the desert sand.

07:20:22.439 --> 07:20:23.880
Breathe fire.

07:20:23.939 --> 07:20:26.040
Queen.

07:20:26.099 --> 07:20:28.979
Since the death of Queen Oasis, the tribe

07:20:28.979 --> 07:20:31.259
is split between 3 rivals for the throne

07:20:31.259 --> 07:20:34.319
sisters burn, blister, and blaze.

07:20:34.380 --> 07:20:36.419
Alliances.

07:20:36.479 --> 07:20:39.720
Burn fights alongside Skywings and

07:20:39.720 --> 07:20:40.380
Mudwings.

07:20:40.500 --> 07:20:43.860
Blister is allied with the sea wings, and

07:20:43.860 --> 07:20:46.259
Blaze has the support of most sand wings

07:20:46.259 --> 07:20:47.639
as well as an alliance with the ice

07:20:47.639 --> 07:20:48.060
wings.

07:20:48.119 --> 07:20:50.880
Mudwings.

07:20:50.939 --> 07:20:54.900
Description, thick armored brown scales

07:20:54.900 --> 07:20:56.159
sometimes with amber and gold

07:20:56.159 --> 07:20:57.000
underscales.

07:20:57.119 --> 07:20:59.880
Large flat heads with nostrils on top of

07:20:59.880 --> 07:21:00.299
the snout.

07:21:00.419 --> 07:21:04.080
Abilities can breathe fire if warm

07:21:04.080 --> 07:21:04.500
enough.

07:21:04.560 --> 07:21:07.619
Hold their breath for up to an hour, blend

07:21:07.619 --> 07:21:09.900
into large mud puddles, usually very

07:21:09.900 --> 07:21:10.200
strong.

07:21:10.259 --> 07:21:13.560
Queen, queen moorhen.

07:21:13.680 --> 07:21:17.400
Alliances, currently allied with burn and

07:21:17.400 --> 07:21:18.659
the sky wings in the Great War.

07:21:18.720 --> 07:21:21.720
Sky Wings.

07:21:21.779 --> 07:21:25.259
Description, red gold or orange scales

07:21:25.259 --> 07:21:26.220
enormous wings.

07:21:26.279 --> 07:21:30.419
Abilities, powerful fighters and flyers

07:21:30.419 --> 07:21:31.680
can breathe fire.

07:21:31.799 --> 07:21:34.560
Queen, Queen Scarlet.

07:21:34.619 --> 07:21:38.639
Alliances, currently allied with burn and

07:21:38.639 --> 07:21:40.020
the mud wings in the Great War.

07:21:40.080 --> 07:21:42.540
Sea wings.

07:21:42.599 --> 07:21:46.380
Description, blue or green or aquamarine

07:21:46.380 --> 07:21:49.740
scales, webs between their claws, gills

07:21:49.740 --> 07:21:52.139
on their necks, glow in the dark stripes

07:21:52.139 --> 07:21:53.880
on their tails, snouts, underbellies.

07:21:53.939 --> 07:21:58.259
Abilities can breathe underwater, see in

07:21:58.259 --> 07:22:00.599
the dark, create huge waves with one

07:22:00.599 --> 07:22:02.040
splash of their powerful tails.

07:22:02.099 --> 07:22:03.779
Excellent swimmers.

07:22:03.900 --> 07:22:09.779
Queen, queen coral, alliances, currently

07:22:09.779 --> 07:22:11.580
allied with blister in the Great War.

07:22:11.700 --> 07:22:16.979
Ice Wings, Description, silvery scales

07:22:16.979 --> 07:22:19.139
like the moon, or pale blue like ice.

07:22:19.200 --> 07:22:23.099
Ridged claws to grip the ice, forked blue

07:22:23.099 --> 07:22:25.740
tongues, tails narrow to a whip thin

07:22:25.740 --> 07:22:26.040
end.

07:22:26.099 --> 07:22:29.939
Abilities, can withstand subzero

07:22:29.939 --> 07:22:31.020
temperatures and bright light.

07:22:31.080 --> 07:22:33.659
Exhale a deadly, freezing breath.

07:22:33.720 --> 07:22:36.540
Queen, Queen Glacier.

07:22:36.599 --> 07:22:38.580
Alliances.

07:22:38.580 --> 07:22:41.340
Currently allied with Blaze and most of

07:22:41.340 --> 07:22:42.540
the sand wings in the Great War.

07:22:42.599 --> 07:22:45.299
Rain wings.

07:22:45.360 --> 07:22:48.419
Description, scales constantly shift

07:22:48.419 --> 07:22:50.220
colors, usually bright like birds of

07:22:50.220 --> 07:22:55.439
paradise, prehensile tails, abilities, can

07:22:55.439 --> 07:22:57.119
camouflage their scales to blend into

07:22:57.119 --> 07:22:57.779
their surroundings.

07:22:57.840 --> 07:23:00.659
Use their prehensile tails for climbing

07:23:00.659 --> 07:23:02.520
no known natural weapons.

07:23:02.580 --> 07:23:05.880
Queen, queen dazzling.

07:23:05.880 --> 07:23:09.599
Alliances, not involved in the Great

07:23:09.599 --> 07:23:09.900
War.

07:23:10.020 --> 07:23:12.599
Night Wings.

07:23:12.659 --> 07:23:14.220
Description.

07:23:14.279 --> 07:23:16.740
Purplish black scales and scattered

07:23:16.740 --> 07:23:18.360
silver scales on the underside of their

07:23:18.360 --> 07:23:20.520
wings, like a night sky full of stars

07:23:20.520 --> 07:23:22.439
forked black tongues.

07:23:22.560 --> 07:23:27.000
Abilities can breathe fire, disappear

07:23:27.000 --> 07:23:30.299
into dark shadows, read minds, foretell

07:23:30.299 --> 07:23:30.659
the future.

07:23:30.659 --> 07:23:34.319
Queen, a closely guarded secret.

07:23:34.380 --> 07:23:38.939
Alliances, too mysterious and powerful to

07:23:38.939 --> 07:23:39.540
be part of the war.
